977.name: 9018-B9 (P92)
977.Applications: Headers, main steam piping and turbine casings, in fossil fuelled power generating plants. Oil refineries and coal liquefaction and gasification plants. Preheat and Interpas temperature 200°C - 300°C.
977.Suitable_For: For matching T/P92, 9%Cr1.7%W0.5%Mo, creep resisting martensitic steels. X10CrWMoVNb 9 2, ASTM: A182 grade F92, A213 grade T92, A335 grade P92, A387 grade 92, 1.4901, NF 616
